=\"https://lihkg.com/t/695900\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/695900</a><br />\nPost 2:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/785703\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/785703</a><br />\nPenana:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/39674\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F39674&d=gCXZhEDRu%2BJLwH3IwIcohuvO%2FPyVe1I8S2KINgfvOuE%3D&h=8acbec1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/39674</a><br />\n<br />\n&lt;&lt;她與他與她&gt;&gt;(未完)<br />\nMiss Chan 話要留我堂幫我補課喎<br />\nPost 1:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/884539\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/884539</a><br />\nPenana:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/41301\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F41301&d=gCXZhEDRu%2BJLwH3IwIcohuvO%2FPyVe1I8S2KINgfvOuE%3D&h=70cdfee2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/41301</a><br />\n<br />\n上面4個同呢個相同世界觀<br />\n下面呢個唔關事<br />\n<br />\n溫緊呈分試，同個戇鳩仔同學吹水嗰陣，佢話佢個明星老母日日都同佢一齊沖涼<br />\nPost:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/801202\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/801202</a>"},{"pid":"2f3cd99db9709323fdd250ae70205e72d01c451c","tid":1413679,"uid":1441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:58:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98efa71a7467d2c9ca955d040b2bea8946774e4d","tid":1413679,"uid":1441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T00:23:59.000Z","msg":"文呢??"},{"pid":"ea19dacf411f313d37b6a11d855f8f4f80191306","tid":1413679,"uid":168703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:09:11.000Z","msg":"雲清我係張居正，會繼續G持你"},{"pid":"687b7f1f08a997bf3a064905118d6e1d1b2561a1","tid":1413679,"uid":45219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T02:58:16.000Z","msg":"可以繼續加更？"},{"pid":"0e50ce2fad031e8d3f3d7d704d800886084812f3","tid":1413679,"uid":10235,"like":0,"dislike